Thank you. Your promotion request for **Alex Mercer (EMP1001)** has been successfully submitted and logged.

Your JIRA Service Management Ticket Key is **HR-8235F**. The HR Review Team will now review the request, focusing on the policy flags triggered during the intake. I have also sent a confirmation email to your management address.

Here is the final summary that was submitted to the HR Review Queue:

