        "variant": "caption"
      },
      {
        "id": "anomaly_1",
        "component": "Text",
        "text": "🔴 **Minimum Pay Violation:** Original proposed rate ($20.00) was below the new job's minimum ($22.00). Rate was automatically corrected to the minimum of $22.00/hr."
      },
      {
        "id": "anomaly_2",
        "component": "Text",
        "text": "⚠️ **High Pay Increase:** The final proposed rate of $22.00/hr is a **33.33% increase**, triggering the >20% Policy Flag for review."
      },
      {
        "id": "manager_justification_text",
        "component": "Text",
        "text": "Justification: Alex has consistently performed at a Store Leader level for the past six months, covering shifts and mentoring other SGAs. The significant raise is justified by this proven high level of performance and retention risk if not compensated appropriately for the new, greater responsibilities."
      }
    ]
  }
}
</a2ui-json>

